<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Website migration]]></title>
  <description><![CDATA[
<p>
Hello! I have at least decided on a static site generator,
<a href="https://github.com/bastibe/org-static-blog">org-static-blog</a>. The tool is pleasantly minimal whilst incorporating
some incredibly useful features, such as the tag system. So this marks
the first page on the new site, and I will begin to migrate content
from the old site posthaste. 
</p>
